parent1.code: A sketch of five brass clockwork robots in the style of steampunk fantasy. They dance gracefully on the surface of a giant pocket watch floating in a swirling vortex of cosmic dust in the depths of space on a starry night, their gears clicking rhythmically, surrounded by constellations and nebulae that pulse with ethereal light.

parent2.code: A whimsical sketch of five brass clockwork robots in the style of fantastical steampunk. They pirouette gracefully on the ornate surface of a colossal pocket watch in the vast depths of space on a starry night, their gears clicking rhythmically, surrounded by shimmering constellations and colorful nebulae.

offspring.code: A watercolor of three iridescent jellyfish-like creatures in the style of bioluminescent fantasy. They undulate hypnotically through the dense underwater forest in the abyssal depths on a moonless night, trailing streams of glowing particles, surrounded by schools of tiny, phosphorescent fish.
